        </trans-unit><trans-unit id="112" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Select the <bpt id="p1">**</bpt>Advanced<ept id="p1">**</ept> tab. Next to the option of <bpt id="p2">**</bpt>Hierarchical namespace<ept id="p2">**</ept>, make sure that the <bpt id="p3">**</bpt>Data lake storage gen2(preview)<ept id="p3">**</ept> option is set to <bpt id="p4">**</bpt>Enabled<ept id="p4">**</ept> as shown below.</source>
